      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "大炮一声绑帐外，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00002",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四大铠、单雄信同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00003",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "不由得豪杰笑开怀。单人独马唐营踹，只杀得儿郎苦悲哀。遍地荒郊血成海，尸骨堆山无有葬埋。小唐童被某",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00004",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "把胆吓坏，二次被擒也应该。今生再不能把节改，要报仇二十年投胎某再来。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00005",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四龙套、李世民、徐勣、罗成、程咬金、尉迟恭同上。〖吹打〗。众人同祭。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00006",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李世民"
      ],
      "text": "看酒来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00007",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "李世民"
      ],
      "text": "一杯酒儿满满酾，尊声将军听言来：王今奉你一斗酒，愿你转世早投胎。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00008",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "唐童假意把我待，花言巧语说开怀。我与你冤仇难分解，报仇还要再投胎。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00009",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "徐勣"
      ],
      "text": "一杯水酒杯中酾，叫声五弟听明白：今日被擒是天意，且莫埋怨愚兄来。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00010",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "徐勣休得巧言盖，阴阳八卦你安排。结义情由你忘怀，你是个人面兽心怀！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00011",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "罗成"
      ],
      "text": "人来看过杯中赛，尊声五哥听开怀：我今奉你一斗酒，愿你魂灵到天台。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00012",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "住口！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00013",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮紧板",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "见罗成把我的牙咬坏，大骂无义小奴才！自从与你来结拜，同心起义巧安排。你到洛阳将某拜，某家接你到家来。我为你招军把兵带，我为你修盖瓦楼台；我为你屯粮把马买，我为你花费许多财；我为你东床招驸马，我为你受了许多灾。你忘恩无义良心败，管叫你乱箭穿身死无有葬埋。",
      "text_length": 126
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00014",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "罗成怒，欲打。程咬金劝。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00015",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "一杯酒儿满满酾，尊一声五哥听明白：你今饮了杯中酒，管叫你灵魂赴天台。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00016",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "赴天台？好，酒来！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00017",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "二杯酒儿杯中酾，小弟言来听开怀：你若饮了二杯酒，保你阴灵到蓬莱。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00018",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "到蓬莱？看酒来！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00019",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "三杯酒，捧上来，我与五哥同心怀。你今饮了三杯酒，将他一个一个俱把刀开，把我丢开。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00020",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "把你丢开？好呀！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00021",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "单雄信"
      ],
      "text": "这句话儿真爽快，叫咬金把酒斟上来。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014011_e00022",
      "play_id": "01014011",
      "scene_id": "01014011_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
